{"entity_id":"npc_group_v2_000001","entity_type":"npc_group","display_name":"村民","aliases":["村民们","村落居民"],"importance":"minor","summary":"村落中的普通居民，以种麦为生。他们使用狼与麦穗的比喻，但这些说法已逐渐失去严肃意义。村民不再需要某种守护，暗示村落文化或社会结构的变化。","evidence_refs":["volume_01-c000-s001-p000001","volume_01-c000-s001-p000003","volume_01-c000-s001-p000010"],"dialogue_count":0,"first_seen_chunk_id":"volume_01-r000001","latest_seen_chunk_id":"volume_01-r000001","relationship_updates":[]}
{"entity_id":"npc_group_v2_000002","entity_type":"npc_group","display_name":"深山村落的村民","aliases":["村民","深山居民"],"importance":"minor","summary":"居住在深山中的普通村民，与罗伦斯进行交易。他们对罗伦斯的到访表示感激，并希望他能再次光顾。虽然未直接参与后续剧情，但他们的存在为罗伦斯的商业活动提供了背景。","evidence_refs":["volume_01-c001-s001-p000025","volume_01-c001-s001-p000026"],"dialogue_count":0,"first_seen_chunk_id":"volume_01-r000003","latest_seen_chunk_id":"volume_01-r000003","relationship_updates":[]}
